itedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:17:54.000Z","msg":"佛家嘅講法係，我地做左感官嘅奴隸，要不停追求外界嘅刺激，但個d刺激實際上係虛幻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:29:19.000Z","msg":"事實係調翻轉，一直精神理想嘅追求都係虛幻，唯有物質給予大腦嘅刺激先會有最強烈嘅感覺。<br />\n<br />\n就好似食抗憂鬱精神科藥物咁，血清素係會加速多巴胺分泌，做乜都可以開心快樂。<br />\n<br />\n宇宙就設計得好好嘅，生物必然要與其他個體交流以證明自己，交流互動間產生無限精彩。<br />\n<br />\n當失去咗感知，就去感知，冇感知又如何認知？<br />\n<br />\n連自己係咩都唔知，談何奴隸不奴隸？"},{"pid":"7ae641ca83f3fec3746f1441b7fca6aecbf28357","tid":685697,"uid":35870,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"9db68d00a73bbb4231a21eb65c1fef06aeff3eb1","tid":685697,"uid":71140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ac046e618b5fdfda810ad44b91ac01aa9bf4ed41","tid":685697,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bb91051661b7934d20f5778f245b81fec243057","tid":685697,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T00:22:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:17:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:36:23.000Z","msg":"佛學呢個咁啱大學take過個course<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都唔算有學識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日都係兩登畀人駁到無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得每個人學習嘅動力都唔同，我細個有時畀人話無禮貌，跟住條氣唔順咪睇下莊子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (因為禮呢個concept儒家，儒家個對家係道家)<br />\n又或者係高登同人嘈，嘈嘈下自己去睇書，睇睇下又幾好睇咪繼續睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ntake佛學course本身係睇唔過眼d佛撚，跟住上堂又同個tutor討論同佢嘈d佛學concept，跟住畀人駁左幾下條氣唔順又自己去睇更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連個tutor都話我咁有興趣，其實我只係對於嗌交有興趣，其實我只係條氣唔順想駁9你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我個人學習嘅動機就係:嗌交<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c88c9b48b2c9db151495b0d7ad460753103271b","tid":685697,"uid":169124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbd83257dca69bfab22eacd71b76e2e4a8630cb9","tid":685697,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbcc18b8f9de0e03cd2cc0cf55cade0ea79426fb","tid":685697,"uid":169124,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T15:40:25.000Z","msg":"可以咁樣一百日，簡直係天堂<br />\n現代嘅正常人生活跟本冇可能有呢種環境同有時間去諗生存以外嘅野<br />\n每日就係要奴役平常人，等佢地跟本冇時間去諗野，咁樣就可以繼續有人幫手做野，呢個社會嘅頂層先得以繼續享樂<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 19999"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:17:54.000Z","msg":"佛家嘅講法係，我地做左感官嘅奴隸，要不停追求外界嘅刺激，但個d刺激實際上係虛幻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"而我反而覺得，人間/生命係獎勵。<br />\n<br />\n可以有機會去貪，享受，去感受 天堂冇痛苦 地獄<br />\n<br />\n冇快樂，而人間就咩都有。<br />\n<br />\n雖然自己講完都覺得on9同自大，但我都係會選擇<br />\n<br />\n爽完再去諗修道。<br />\n<br />\n人生一世咩都要試，但我諗咁樣諗法嘅人大有人<br />\n<br />\n在，而結果就係泥足深陷，最後已經唔會記得要<br />\n<br />\n空。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7724dcd02f9dee7008a69630e7d0f17d0be2a6e3","tid":685697,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T15:50:12.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e84d5efb511126abc9c24c315badffebccf9e497","tid":685697,"uid":10287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9db68d00a73bbb4231a21eb65c1fef06aeff3eb1","tid":685697,"uid":71140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ac046e618b5fdfda810ad44b91ac01aa9bf4ed41","tid":685697,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bb91051661b7934d20f5778f245b81fec243057","tid":685697,"uid":71140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T00:22:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:15:48.